                <note rend="inline" type="source">758.6114AI/135a: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Acting Secretary of State</gloss> to
                        the Ambassador in France</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Wallace</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1920-10-09T14:00:00-04:00">
                            <hi rend="italic">October 9, 1920—2 p.m.</hi>
                        </date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>1546. Your 1778, October 5, 9 p.m.</p>
                <p>You may informally advise Professor Mantoux that the President would consider
                    favorably request to nominate an American for appointment on the Committee.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Davis</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
